1. Problem
Students had full control over lab PCs.

2. Process
Create GPO in AD

3. Link to “Lab Computers OU”

4. Configure:
Disable Control Panel
Block CMD/PowerShell
Disable USB storage
Apply gpupdate /force

5. Pros
Prevents misuse
Stable lab environment

6. Cons
Over-restriction affects learning
Troubleshooting harder for IT staff

7. Cost
Free (built into Windows Server)
